item.title: 1 Error n_n <3<3<3<3
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

“Object” without any sort of qualifier, defaults to java.lang.Object, which is in no way related to RuneScape objects.

You can either change the class name, to “WorldObject” or “GameObject”, otherwise you’ll have to say


new server.model.objects.Object(blah, blah, blah);
